value.text: ...in a kingdom cloaked in emerald forests and crowned with snow-capped mountains, there lived a young woman named Elara. She possessed hair like spun moonlight and eyes that shimmered with the secrets of the ancient woods.  But Elara harbored a secret of her own, one that whispered on the wind and danced in the shadows...
